Package: ggiraph
Type: Package
Title: Make 'ggplot' Graphics Interactive Using 'htmlwidgets'
Description: Create interactive ggplot graphics that are usable in the 'RStudio'
    viewer pane, in 'R Markdown' documents, and in 'Shiny' apps.
